We are committed to safeguarding the privacy of the users of our Services; this policy sets out
            how we will treat your personal information.
Your use of our Services is subject to your acceptance of the Terms of Service and this policy. If
            you disagree with any provisions of either document, you must not use our Services.
(1) Information we collect
We may collect, store and use the following kinds of personal information.
(a) Information you provide. This includes your account information (email address
                and password), information about your learning preferences, and demographic
                information. If you subscribe to our paid Services, then weâ€™ll request additional
                information, including your full name and payment method details.
(b) Data we gather. This includes data about your computer and about your visits to
