(e) if you have specifically agreed to this, send to you marketing communications
                (you can inform us at any time if you no longer wish to receive marketing
                communications);
(f) provide third parties with statistical information about our user base â€“ but this
                information will not be used to identify any individual user;
(g) collect payments from you; and
(h) maintain records of our business transactions as required by applicable law.
If you submit your personal information as part of your user content, we will publish and
            otherwise use that information in accordance with the license you grant to us.
We may use the data we gather, and non-personally identifiable demographical data you
            provide, to create derived data, algorithm improvements, or other â€œderivative informationâ€.
            You expressly agree that such derivative information is no longer considered your personal
            information, and that you will have no claims whatsoever as regards such derivative information.
Upon termination of your user account for whatever reason, we will:
(a) immediately and permanently delete from our active databases your account
